{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-73-counting-fractions-in-a-range","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 73: Brojanje elemenata u nizu","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Razmotrite deo, $\\frac{n}{d}$, gde su <code>n</code> i <code>d</code> pozitivni ceo broj. Ako je <code>n</code> &#x3C; <code>d</code> sa najvećim zajedničkim parametrom, ${HCF}(n, d) = 1$, zvaničito se naziva pojednostavljeni tačan deo.</p>\n<p>Ako navedemo skup tačnih pojednostavljenih delova za <code>d</code> ≤ 8 u rastućem redosledu veličine, dobijamo:</p>\n<p>$$\\frac{1}{8}, \\frac{1}{7}, \\frac{1}{6}, \\frac{1}{5}, \\frac{1}{4}, \\frac{2}{7}, \\frac{1}{3}, \\mathbf{\\frac{3}{8}, \\frac{2}{5}, \\frac{3}{7}}, \\frac{1}{2}, \\frac{4}{7}, \\frac{3}{5}, \\frac{5}{8}, \\frac{2}{3}, \\frac{5}{7}, \\frac{3}{4}, \\frac{4}{5}, \\frac{5}{6}, \\frac{6}{7}, \\frac{7}{8}$$</p>\n<p>Izgleda da postoji deo <code>3</code> između $\\frac{1}{3}$ i $\\frac{1}{2}$.</p>\n<p>Koliko se razlomaka nalazi između $\\frac{1}{3}$ i $\\frac{1}{2}$ u uređenom skupu pravilno skraćenih razlomaka za <code>d</code> ≤ <code>limit</code>?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3b61000cf542c50fec8","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302186,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-73-counting-fractions-in-a-range"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function countingFractionsInARange(limit) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ncountingFractionsInARange(8);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"